languages.text: {n}Тело эльдарки покрывают серьезные раны, а звуки редкого, угасающего дыхания едва доносятся до ваших ушей. Ирлиэт с трудом удается подняться на колени, но смотрит она вовсе не на Винтерскейла — полный ненависти взгляд прикован лишь к вашему лицу.{/n}

{n}Yrliet's body is covered in grave wounds, and her shallow, infrequent breathing is barely audible. She struggles to her knees, but she does not look at Calligos — her gaze, brimming with hatred, is trained on you.{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}The Aeldari's body is covered in grave wounds, and her shallow, infrequent breathing is barely audible. She struggles to her knees, but her hateful gaze is not fixed on Winterscale — it is trained on your face.{/n}

languages.text: {n}El cuerpo de Yrliet está cubierto de heridas graves, y su respiración ardua e irregular es apenas perceptible. Yrliet lucha por ponerse de rodillas; pero no mira a Winterscale. Su mirada, rebosante de odio, está dirigida solo hacia ti.{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}Yrliet's body is covered in grave wounds, and her shallow, infrequent breathing is barely audible. She struggles to her knees, but she does not look at Calligos — her gaze, brimming with hatred, is trained on you.{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}El cuerpo de la Aeldari está cubierto de heridas graves, y su respiración ardua e irregular es apenas perceptible. Yrliet lucha por ponerse de rodillas; pero en vez de clavar su mirada de odio en Winterscale, te mira a ti, directamente a los ojos.{/n}

languages.text: {n}伊莉耶特遍体鳞伤，你几乎听不见她短促而微弱呼吸。她挣扎着跪在地上，但她充满仇恨的目光并没有看向卡里戈斯，而是盯着你的脸。{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}Yrliet's body is covered in grave wounds, and her shallow, infrequent breathing is barely audible. She struggles to her knees, but she does not look at Calligos — her gaze, brimming with hatred, is trained on you.{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}伊莉耶特遍体鳞伤，你几乎听不见她短促而微弱呼吸。她挣扎着跪在地上，但她充满仇恨的目光并没有看向温特斯凯尔，而是盯着你的脸。{/n}

languages.text: {n}Le corps d'Yrliet est couvert de terribles blessures et sa respiration saccadée est à peine audible. Alors qu'elle peine à se mettre à genoux, ce n'est pas Winterscale qu'elle fixe d'un regard haineux, mais vous.{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}Yrliet's body is covered in grave wounds, and her shallow, infrequent breathing is barely audible. She struggles to her knees, but she does not look at Calligos — her gaze, brimming with hatred, is trained on you.{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}Le corps de l'Aeldari est couvert de graves blessures et sa respiration saccadée est à peine audible. Alors qu'elle essaie tant bien que mal de se mettre à genoux, ce n'est pas Winterscale qu'Yrliet fixe d'un regard haineux, mais vous.{/n}

languages.text: {n}ユリエットの身体は満身創痍で、浅く少ない呼吸がかろうじて聞こえる程度だ。彼女は膝をついて、その憎悪に満ちた眼差しはカリゴスではなく、あなたの顔に向けられている。{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}Yrliet's body is covered in grave wounds, and her shallow, infrequent breathing is barely audible. She struggles to her knees, but she does not look at Calligos — her gaze, brimming with hatred, is trained on you.{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}アエルダリの身体は満身創痍で、浅く少ない呼吸がかろうじて聞こえる程度だ。ユリエットは膝をついて、もがいているものの、その憎悪に満ちた眼差しはウィンタースケールではなく、あなたの顔に向けられている。{/n}

languages.text: {n}Yrliets Körper ist mit schweren Wunden übersät, und ihr flacher, unregelmäßiger Atem ist kaum mehr zu hören. Sie müht sich auf die Knie, doch sie blickt nicht Calligos an. Ihr hasserfüllter Blick ist auf dich gerichtet.{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}Yrliet's body is covered in grave wounds, and her shallow, infrequent breathing is barely audible. She struggles to her knees, but she does not look at Calligos — her gaze, brimming with hatred, is trained on you.{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}Der Körper der Aeldari ist mit schweren Wunden übersät, und ihr seichter, unregelmäßiger Atem ist kaum mehr zu hören. Yrliet geht mühsam auf die Knie, doch ihr hasserfüllter Blick ist nicht auf Winterzunder gerichtet, sondern auf dein Gesicht.{/n}
